editor

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • editor.ObjectCollection
      • editor.Matrix
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BWFrame, ColorFrame

    public class Matrix
extends ObjectCollection

    MATRIX

    Class that represents a Matrix as an array of vectors, where each column is represented as a Vector Note: Matrix inherits from Object collection and it is generated as a "template" so it has a max dimension, and then by passing the number of rows and columns by its constructor we define its real dimensions
